author: sussman
msg: Regression fix:  make mod_dav_svn notice svn:mime-type again on public URIs.

overzealous.  'regular' resources can have mime-types too, not just
'version' ones.

msg: Make ra->get_dir work in perl bindings. Also update build instructions.
* perl/Core.pm: Add class wrapper for svn_dirent_t.
